            <div class="fs-18 fw-bold f-nunito text-red">
              Non-Discrimination
            </div>
            <p>
              Businesses cannot discriminate against residents for exercising their rights under the CCPA. This means
              that businesses cannot charge different prices or provide different levels of service based on a
              resident's exercise of their rights.
            </p>
          </div>
